Abbas Says U.K., France Would Recognize State, Haaretz Reports

-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 
2011-04-20T06:04:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/abbas-says-u-k-france-would-recognize-state-haaretz-reports.html
Palestinian Authority President
 Mahmoud Abbas  said the U.K. and  France  would recognize a
unilaterally declared Palestinian state within the 1967 borders,
Haaretz reported, citing an interview with Abbas in the
Palestinian daily Al-Ayyam.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
